s:429:"<p>Here is how <span><span><span>finance</span> </span></span>is <span><span>important</span> </span>to business: Initial Capital: It is popularly said that money is essential for making money. To start the activities of a business, capital investment is required. Proper short-term <span><span>financial</span> </span>planning and maintenance of good working capital flow is crucial to keep the operations going.<br /></p>";